    <h2>Why this survey</h2>

    <p>The <a href="/reading/cognitive-architecture/vaswani-2017/">transformer paper</a> gives you the architecture. This survey gives you everything built on top: how models are trained, aligned, prompted, evaluated, compressed, and deployed. Four pillars, each a stage in the lifecycle of an LLM.</p>

    <h2>The four pillars</h2>

    <div class="overflow-x-auto">
      <table class="w-full text-sm">
        <thead>
          <tr class="border-b border-zinc-700">
