          <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800"><td class="py-2 pr-3 text-gray-300">Post-training</td><td class="pr-3 text-gray-400">Instruction tuning (SFT), alignment tuning (RLHF and alternatives), parameter-efficient adaptation (LoRA, adapters)</td><td class="text-gray-400">§5</td></tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800"><td class="py-2 pr-3 text-gray-300">Utilization</td><td class="pr-3 text-gray-400">Prompt engineering, in-context learning, chain-of-thought reasoning, planning and agentic frameworks</td><td class="text-gray-400">§6</td></tr>
